Tell Me More

Services

A picture is worth a thousand words, but a 3D model is worth a million.

3D Models

Collect 3D models of famous and historic landmarks. These 3D models form your Travel Trails collection. Relive your memories by interacting with the high resolution models and exploring sites like you've never seen before.

Crowd Sourced

Gone are the days where expensive LiDAR equipment is needed to create 3D models. You can contribute your images to free, crowd sourced 3D models. Your images are used to add detail and fill holes in the model.

Social

Connect with your friends and travel community. Check out places they have visited and draw inspiration for your next adventure.

Models

A few samples of models generated with Travel Trails! Click and drag to interact.
